### 브랜드 가입 신청 (브랜드 + BRAND_ADMIN 동시 생성)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/signup/brand
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "brandName": "메가커피",
  "businessNo": "123-45-67890",
  "commissionRate": 10.0,
  "adminEmail": "mega@test.com",
  "adminPassword": "password123",
  "adminName": "브랜드관리자",
  "adminPhone": "010-1234-5678"
}

### 회원가입 (STORE_OWNER / ENGINEER)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "store@test.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "name": "매장주",
  "phone": "010-1234-5678",
  "role": "STORE_OWNER",
  "brandId": 1
}

### 로그인 (SUPER_ADMIN)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@run4you.com",
  "password": "admin1234!"
}

