### 브랜드 목록 조회 (SUPER_ADMIN)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/brands
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 브랜드 승인 (SUPER_ADMIN)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/brands/1/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 브랜드 거절 (SUPER_ADMIN)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/brands/1/reject
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 수수료율 변경 (SUPER_ADMIN)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/brands/1/commission-rate
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "commissionRate": 15.0
}

### 승인 대기 유저 목록 (SUPER_ADMIN)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/pending
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 전체 유저 목록 (SUPER_ADMIN)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 유저 승인 (SUPER_ADMIN)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/users/1/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 유저 거절 (SUPER_ADMIN)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/users/1/reject
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
